# NOTE — the generated design-system artifacts are intentionally COMMITTED:
#   _ds_bundle.js · _ds_manifest.json · _adherence.oxlintrc.json
# The component cards + UI kits load _ds_bundle.js, so keeping them lets the
# Design System tab / cards render outside the design tool. Delete these lines
# (and the files) only if you want a pure-source skill with no prebuilt bundle.
